Select 'tblProductMaster' AS TableName, count(*) AS RecordCount from tblProductMaster
UNION ALL
Select 'tblVendorCategory' AS TableName, count(*) AS RecordCount from tblVendorCategory
UNION ALL
Select 'tblProductVendorCat' AS TableName, count(*) AS RecordCount from tblProductVendorCat
UNION ALL
Select 'tbl_Vendor_VendorCat' AS TableName, count(*) AS RecordCount from tbl_Vendor_VendorCat
GO 


IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tblProductMaster WHERE ProductName = '') 
BEGIN
IF(''<>'')
INSERT INTO tblProductMaster (ProductName) VALUES ('')
END
GO

IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = '') 
BEGIN
IF('' <> '')
INSERT INTO tblVendorCategory (VendorCategoryNm, IsRetail_Wholesale, IsManufacturer) VALUES ('', null,null)
END
ELSE 
BEGIN
UPDATE tblVendorCategory SET IsRetail_Wholesale=null, IsManufacturer=null  WHERE VendorCategoryNm = ''; 
END
GO

INSERT INTO tblVendorCategory (VendorCategoryNm, IsRetail_Wholesale, IsManufacturer) VALUES ('High Lift Rental', 1,0)
END
ELSE 
BEGIN
UPDATE tblVendorCategory SET IsRetail_Wholesale=1, IsManufacturer=0  WHERE VendorCategoryNm = 'High Lift Rental'; 
END
GO

BEGIN
UPDATE tblVendorCategory SET IsRetail_Wholesale=1, IsManufacturer=0  WHERE VendorCategoryNm = 'Iron railing supply'; 
END

INSERT INTO tblVendorCategory (VendorCategoryNm, IsRetail_Wholesale, IsManufacturer) VALUES ('Auto Repair and Body', 1,0)
END
ELSE 
BEGIN
UPDATE tblVendorCategory SET IsRetail_Wholesale=1, IsManufacturer=0  WHERE VendorCategoryNm = 'Auto Repair and Body'; 
END
GO

INSERT INTO tblVendorCategory (VendorCategoryNm, IsRetail_Wholesale, IsManufacturer) VALUES ('Hardwood Laminate Ba', 1,0)
END
ELSE 
BEGIN
UPDATE tblVendorCategory SET IsRetail_Wholesale=1, IsManufacturer=0  WHERE VendorCategoryNm = 'Hardwood Laminate Ba'; 
END

IF('' <> '')
INSERT INTO tblVendorCategory (VendorCategoryNm, IsRetail_Wholesale, IsManufacturer) VALUES ('', null,null)
END
ELSE 
BEGIN
UPDATE tblVendorCategory SET IsRetail_Wholesale=null, IsManufacturer=null  WHERE VendorCategoryNm = ''; 
END
GO

IF('' <> '')
INSERT INTO tblVendorCategory (VendorCategoryNm, IsRetail_Wholesale, IsManufacturer) VALUES ('', null,null)
END
ELSE 
BEGIN
UPDATE tblVendorCategory SET IsRetail_Wholesale=null, IsManufacturer=null  WHERE VendorCategoryNm = ''; 
END
GO

IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = 'cabinet manufacturer') 
BEGIN
IF('cabinet manufacturer' <> '')
INSERT INTO tblVendorCategory (VendorCategoryNm, IsRetail_Wholesale, IsManufacturer) VALUES ('cabinet manufacturer', 0,1)
END
ELSE 
BEGIN
UPDATE tblVendorCategory SET IsRetail_Wholesale=0, IsManufacturer=1  WHERE VendorCategoryNm = 'cabinet manufacturer'; 
END

INSERT INTO tblVendorCategory (VendorCategoryNm, IsRetail_Wholesale, IsManufacturer) VALUES ('', null,null)
END
ELSE 
BEGIN

END

INSERT INTO tblVendorCategory (VendorCategoryNm, IsRetail_Wholesale, IsManufacturer) VALUES ('', 1,null)
END
ELSE 
BEGIN
UPDATE tblVendorCategory SET IsRetail_Wholesale=1, IsManufacturer=null  WHERE VendorCategoryNm = ''; 
END
GO
IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = '') 
BEGIN
IF('' <> '')
INSERT INTO tblVendorCategory (VendorCategoryNm, IsRetail_Wholesale, IsManufacturer) VALUES ('', 0,null)
END
ELSE 
BEGIN
UPDATE tblVendorCategory SET IsRetail_Wholesale=0, IsManufacturer=null  WHERE VendorCategoryNm = ''; 
END
GO
IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = '') 
BEGIN
IF('' <> '')
INSERT INTO tblVendorCategory (VendorCategoryNm, IsRetail_Wholesale, IsManufacturer) VALUES ('', 1,null)
END
ELSE 
BEGIN
UPDATE tblVendorCategory SET IsRetail_Wholesale=1, IsManufacturer=null  WHERE VendorCategoryNm = ''; 
END
GO
IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = '') 
BEGIN
IF('' <> '')
INSERT INTO tblVendorCategory (VendorCategoryNm, IsRetail_Wholesale, IsManufacturer) VALUES ('', 1,null)
END
ELSE 
BEGIN
UPDATE tblVendorCategory SET IsRetail_Wholesale=1, IsManufacturer=null  WHERE VendorCategoryNm = ''; 
END
GO

DECLARE @ProductID INT 
DECLARE @VendorCatID INT 
Select @ProductID=ProductId from tblProductMaster WHERE ProductName = ''
Select @VendorCatID=VendorCategpryId from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = ''
IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tblProductVendorCat WHERE ProductCategoryId=@ProductID AND VendorCategoryId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
IF(''<>'' AND ''<>'')
INSERT INTO tblProductVendorCat (ProductCategoryId,VendorCategoryId) VALUES (@ProductID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

Select @ProductID=ProductId from tblProductMaster WHERE ProductName = 'Gutters & Gutter Guards'
Select @VendorCatID=VendorCategpryId from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = ''
IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tblProductVendorCat WHERE ProductCategoryId=@ProductID AND VendorCategoryId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
IF(''<>'' AND 'Gutters & Gutter Guards'<>'')
INSERT INTO tblProductVendorCat (ProductCategoryId,VendorCategoryId) VALUES (@ProductID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

DECLARE @VendorCatID INT 
Select @ProductID=ProductId from tblProductMaster WHERE ProductName = 'Equipment & Industry'
Select @VendorCatID=VendorCategpryId from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = 'High Lift Rental'
IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tblProductVendorCat WHERE ProductCategoryId=@ProductID AND VendorCategoryId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
IF('High Lift Rental'<>'' AND 'Equipment & Industry'<>'')
INSERT INTO tblProductVendorCat (ProductCategoryId,VendorCategoryId) VALUES (@ProductID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

INSERT INTO tblProductVendorCat (ProductCategoryId,VendorCategoryId) VALUES (@ProductID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

Select @ProductID=ProductId from tblProductMaster WHERE ProductName = 'Kitchens'
Select @VendorCatID=VendorCategpryId from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = 'Kitchen Cabinet Supp'
IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tblProductVendorCat WHERE ProductCategoryId=@ProductID AND VendorCategoryId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
IF('Kitchen Cabinet Supp'<>'' AND 'Kitchens'<>'')
INSERT INTO tblProductVendorCat (ProductCategoryId,VendorCategoryId) VALUES (@ProductID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO
DECLARE @ProductID INT 
DECLARE @VendorCatID INT 
Select @ProductID=ProductId from tblProductMaster WHERE ProductName = 'Framing- Drywall-Insulation-trim'
Select @VendorCatID=VendorCategpryId from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = ''
IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tblProductVendorCat WHERE ProductCategoryId=@ProductID AND VendorCategoryId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
IF(''<>'' AND 'Framing- Drywall-Insulation-trim'<>'')
INSERT INTO tblProductVendorCat (ProductCategoryId,VendorCategoryId) VALUES (@ProductID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tblProductVendorCat WHERE ProductCategoryId=@ProductID AND VendorCategoryId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
IF('Iron railing supply'<>'' AND 'Fencing'<>'')
INSERT INTO tblProductVendorCat (ProductCategoryId,VendorCategoryId) VALUES (@ProductID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tblProductVendorCat WHERE ProductCategoryId=@ProductID AND VendorCategoryId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
IF(''<>'' AND ''<>'')
INSERT INTO tblProductVendorCat (ProductCategoryId,VendorCategoryId) VALUES (@ProductID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

DECLARE @VendorCatID INT

BEGIN
IF('Auto Repair and Body'<>'' AND 'Overhead'<>'')
INSERT INTO tblProductVendorCat (ProductCategoryId,VendorCategoryId) VALUES (@ProductID,@VendorCatID)
END

DECLARE @VendorCatID INT 
Select @ProductID=ProductId from tblProductMaster WHERE ProductName = 'Electric'
Select @VendorCatID=VendorCategpryId from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = 'Electric Supply'
IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tblProductVendorCat WHERE ProductCategoryId=@ProductID AND VendorCategoryId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
IF('Electric Supply'<>'' AND 'Electric'<>'')
INSERT INTO tblProductVendorCat (ProductCategoryId,VendorCategoryId) VALUES (@ProductID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tblProductVendorCat WHERE ProductCategoryId=@ProductID AND VendorCategoryId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
IF('appliances distribut'<>'' AND 'Kitchens'<>'')
INSERT INTO tblProductVendorCat (ProductCategoryId,VendorCategoryId) VALUES (@ProductID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tblProductVendorCat WHERE ProductCategoryId=@ProductID AND VendorCategoryId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
IF(''<>'' AND ''<>'')
INSERT INTO tblProductVendorCat (ProductCategoryId,VendorCategoryId) VALUES (@ProductID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

DECLARE @ProductID INT 
DECLARE @VendorCatID INT 
Select @ProductID=ProductId from tblProductMaster WHERE ProductName = 'Windows & Doors'
Select @VendorCatID=VendorCategpryId from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = 'Doors Windows Manuf'
IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tblProductVendorCat WHERE ProductCategoryId=@ProductID AND VendorCategoryId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
IF('Doors Windows Manuf'<>'' AND 'Windows & Doors'<>'')
INSERT INTO tblProductVendorCat (ProductCategoryId,VendorCategoryId) VALUES (@ProductID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

Select @ProductID=ProductId from tblProductMaster WHERE ProductName = 'Windows & Doors'
Select @VendorCatID=VendorCategpryId from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = 'Doors Windows Manuf'
IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tblProductVendorCat WHERE ProductCategoryId=@ProductID AND VendorCategoryId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
IF('Doors Windows Manuf'<>'' AND 'Windows & Doors'<>'')
INSERT INTO tblProductVendorCat (ProductCategoryId,VendorCategoryId) VALUES (@ProductID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

INSERT INTO tblProductVendorCat (ProductCategoryId,VendorCategoryId) VALUES (@ProductID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

DECLARE @VendorCatID INT

Select @VendorCatID=VendorCategpryId from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = ''
IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tblProductVendorCat WHERE ProductCategoryId=@ProductID AND VendorCategoryId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
IF(''<>'' AND ''<>'')
INSERT INTO tblProductVendorCat (ProductCategoryId,VendorCategoryId) VALUES (@ProductID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tblProductVendorCat WHERE ProductCategoryId=@ProductID AND VendorCategoryId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
IF('Cabinet Manufacturer'<>'' AND 'Kitchens'<>'')
INSERT INTO tblProductVendorCat (ProductCategoryId,VendorCategoryId) VALUES (@ProductID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

DECLARE @VendorCatID INT 
Select @ProductID=ProductId from tblProductMaster WHERE ProductName = 'overhead'
Select @VendorCatID=VendorCategpryId from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = 'signs & lettering'
IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tblProductVendorCat WHERE ProductCategoryId=@ProductID AND VendorCategoryId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
IF('signs & lettering'<>'' AND 'overhead'<>'')
INSERT INTO tblProductVendorCat (ProductCategoryId,VendorCategoryId) VALUES (@ProductID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

IF(''<>'' AND 'tool-equipment'<>'')
INSERT INTO tblProductVendorCat (ProductCategoryId,VendorCategoryId) VALUES (@ProductID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

DECLARE @VendorCatID INT 
Select @VendorID=VendorId from tblvendors WHERE VendorName = 'J & L Materials'
Select @VendorCatID=VendorCategpryId from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = ''
IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tbl_Vendor_VendorCat WHERE VendorId=@VendorID AND VendorCatId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
if('J & L Materials'<>'' AND ''<>'')
INSERT INTO tbl_Vendor_VendorCat (VendorId,VendorCatId) VALUES (@VendorID,@VendorCatID)
END

Select @VendorID=VendorId from tblvendors WHERE VendorName = 'Reedman Auto toll'
Select @VendorCatID=VendorCategpryId from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = 'Passenger Van'
IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tbl_Vendor_VendorCat WHERE VendorId=@VendorID AND VendorCatId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
if('Reedman Auto toll'<>'' AND 'Passenger Van'<>'')
INSERT INTO tbl_Vendor_VendorCat (VendorId,VendorCatId) VALUES (@VendorID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

Select @VendorCatID=VendorCategpryId from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = ''
IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tbl_Vendor_VendorCat WHERE VendorId=@VendorID AND VendorCatId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
if('all state '<>'' AND ''<>'')
INSERT INTO tbl_Vendor_VendorCat (VendorId,VendorCatId) VALUES (@VendorID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

DECLARE @VendorCatID INT 
Select @VendorID=VendorId from tblvendors WHERE VendorName = 'L & T Stone and Kitchen Supply'
Select @VendorCatID=VendorCategpryId from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = 'Kitchen Cabinet Supp'
IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tbl_Vendor_VendorCat WHERE VendorId=@VendorID AND VendorCatId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
if('L & T Stone and Kitchen Supply'<>'' AND 'Kitchen Cabinet Supp'<>'')
INSERT INTO tbl_Vendor_VendorCat (VendorId,VendorCatId) VALUES (@VendorID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

DECLARE @VendorCatID INT 
Select @VendorID=VendorId from tblvendors WHERE VendorName = 'B.G halko and sons'
Select @VendorCatID=VendorCategpryId from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = 'fencing aluminium'
IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tbl_Vendor_VendorCat WHERE VendorId=@VendorID AND VendorCatId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
if('B.G halko and sons'<>'' AND 'fencing aluminium'<>'')
INSERT INTO tbl_Vendor_VendorCat (VendorId,VendorCatId) VALUES (@VendorID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

Select @VendorCatID=VendorCategpryId from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = 'Doors Windows Manuf'
IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tbl_Vendor_VendorCat WHERE VendorId=@VendorID AND VendorCatId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
if('Zeluck'<>'' AND 'Doors Windows Manuf'<>'')
INSERT INTO tbl_Vendor_VendorCat (VendorId,VendorCatId) VALUES (@VendorID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

Select @VendorID=VendorId from tblvendors WHERE VendorName = 'Inter Ceramic'
Select @VendorCatID=VendorCategpryId from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = ''
IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tbl_Vendor_VendorCat WHERE VendorId=@VendorID AND VendorCatId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
if('Inter Ceramic'<>'' AND ''<>'')
INSERT INTO tbl_Vendor_VendorCat (VendorId,VendorCatId) VALUES (@VendorID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

Select @VendorID=VendorId from tblvendors WHERE VendorName = 'Chester County KItch and Bath'
Select @VendorCatID=VendorCategpryId from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = ''
IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tbl_Vendor_VendorCat WHERE VendorId=@VendorID AND VendorCatId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
if('Chester County KItch and Bath'<>'' AND ''<>'')
INSERT INTO tbl_Vendor_VendorCat (VendorId,VendorCatId) VALUES (@VendorID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

Select @VendorID=VendorId from tblvendors WHERE VendorName = 'Ace Hardware'
Select @VendorCatID=VendorCategpryId from tblVendorCategory WHERE VendorCategoryNm = ''
IF NOT EXISTS (Select * from tbl_Vendor_VendorCat WHERE VendorId=@VendorID AND VendorCatId = @VendorCatID) 
BEGIN
if('Ace Hardware'<>'' AND ''<>'')
INSERT INTO tbl_Vendor_VendorCat (VendorId,VendorCatId) VALUES (@VendorID,@VendorCatID)
END
GO

Select 'tblProductMaster' AS TableName, count(*) AS RecordCount from tblProductMaster
UNION ALL
Select 'tblVendorCategory' AS TableName, count(*) AS RecordCount from tblVendorCategory
UNION ALL
Select 'tblProductVendorCat' AS TableName, count(*) AS RecordCount from tblProductVendorCat
UNION ALL
Select 'tbl_Vendor_VendorCat' AS TableName, count(*) AS RecordCount from tbl_Vendor_VendorCat
GO
